Document: ResourceImporter  
Path: godot/classes/class_resourceimporter.rst  
Summary: Base class for Godot's resource importers, providing functionality for importing external resources into the engine.  

This is the base class for Godot's resource importers. To implement your own resource importers using editor plugins, see EditorImportPlugin. Note: Custom importers must inherit from this class and override its methods to handle specific file formats and import logic. The class defines core behaviors for parsing, validating, and converting external resources into Godot-compatible formats. Key Rule: All resource importers must implement the import method to process files and generate runtime assets.
